{"tid":1069494,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突然覺得......自己其實一個朋友都冇","createTime":"2019-03-20T04:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T04:22:32.000Z","uid":112142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6660995cb3c49643692bf1d2b073aafc338b11ef","tid":1069494,"uid":112142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T04:22:32.000Z","msg":"細佬今年23歲<br />\n早排考左電單車牌<br />\n有時一班人出車好似好開心咁<br />\n但總係融入唔到佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前既朋友大家都忙，少左聯絡<br />\n有時想搵一個人傾下計都冇<br />\n<br />\n行出街見到其他男男女女都一對對<br />\n就覺得自己有d悲哀<br />\n咁大個人都係拍過一次拖<br />\n<br />\n總覺得人與人之間嘅接觸好攰....<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鳩噏完<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}